            <main role="main" class=""><article class="main-content"><h1 class="">News</h1>
        <p class="">There’s always something interesting happening in Conemaugh Township. On this page, we’ll post details about upcoming events, past activities, school awards, and much more—so bookmark this page and check back often!</p>
        
        <div class="pom-container">
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="ElementaryContinuityofEducationPickupPlans"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">Elementary Continuity of Education Pickup Plans - May 1 and 2</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><p class="">It is time for us to collect completed work, PTA fundraiser money, library books, 5th-grade grammar books, and other items to be returned to the school. We will also distribute the next round of learning activities that will cover May 4 through May 15. These deliveries and pickups will be on May 1 and 2. Please see our <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_396870/site_396871/Documents/Elementary-Packet-Pickup.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">continuity of education pickup plans document</a> for details.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="ContinuityofEducationPlan"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">Continuity of Education Plan</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><p class="">Please review our <a href="https://www.ctasd.org/Continuity-of-Education" title="" alt="" target="_self">Continuity of Education page</a> for information on instruction during our school building closures.</p></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="supportlineflyer"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">COVID-19 Support Line</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class=""><p class="">The Pennsylvania Department of Human Resources has created a hotline available 24 hours per day, seven days per week, for those who may be struggling with the enforced isolation. The hotline can be used for help coping with anxiety and difficult emotions, assistance accessing area resources, and information regarding health and safety updates. Please read our <a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_396870/site_396871/Documents/Covid19-Support-Line-Flyer.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">hotline flyer</a> for more information and call (855) 284-2494 if you need support.</p></div></div>
</div>
<div class="newsItem">
<a name="coronavirus"></a>
	<div class="newstitle">Coronavirus Disease 2019 (COVID-19)</div>
	<div class="newsbody"><div class="">
<p class="">Coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) is a new respiratory virus first identified in Wuhan, Hubei Province, China. It is part of a larger family of viruses called coronavirus, some of which are in circulation normally and can cause illnesses like the common cold. We invite you to visit the resources below for more information.</p>
<p class=""></p>
<ul>
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_396870/site_396871/Documents/Share-Facts-About-COVID-19.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">Share Facts About COVID-19</a></li>
<li class=""><a href="https://tb2cdn.schoolwebmasters.com/accnt_396870/site_396871/Documents/What-to-Do-if-Sick-with-COVID-19.pdf" title="" alt="" target="_blank">What to Do if You are Sick with COVID-19</a></li>
</ul>
</div></div>
</div>
</div>
